  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whenever the train was stopping here and there, we will go and pinch, and steal food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were passing through all travel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We would steal-- they were the beautiful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was September.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was beautiful cherries in the trees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were taking apples, whatever you found, just-- and that is what we ate, you know, during the train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was no food for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, you know, the train went to Prague, went to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It went to all the places it was stopping.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But, I must tell you, wherever we went, we found the Red Cross very-- the Red Cross, they were always waiting in the trains for-- they don't know who was passing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Whoever was passing, they were little bit of basket to give an apple or so to this prisoner.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, eventually, we arrived to a place, you know, that there were all the Italians there, going to Italy, the prisoner, Italians.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Not only that, the other Jewish-- Jewish people that had escaped from other camps ready to go to Italy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In the meantime, it was already September.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The war had already finished, you know, a few months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we joined this thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we went through the Brenner Road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Brenner Road is through the Alps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Like you say, the Alps in Italy, we went through the Brenner Road.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we arrive in Italy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We arrived to Italy because we were meant to go to Rhodes Island, back where we came.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then, to go-- the Brenner Road is in the Italy of north.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "To go to Rhodes Island, we have to go all day Italy until it comes to the south, to take a boat to go to Rhodes Island, because you cannot go-- it's an island.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
